/* sovir/mathesis_chi_main.iii -- THE CHI STREAM DRIVER (campaign Chi: the capability lift).
 * Prints the big judge's discharge of the 12 refusals + the exact ordering, the full fourth
 * token census, the pattern instrument's tables/verdicts, and the pilot's rounds 12..17.
 * Sealed as DOCS/MATHESIS-CHI-ROUND1.log; replay must be byte-identical. */
module mathesis_chi_main

